### Search Materials by Name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/materials/search?keyword=cement HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

### Search Materials by Price Range
GET http://localhost:8080/api/materials/search?minPrice=100&maxPrice=500 HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

### Search Materials by Name and Price Range
GET http://localhost:8080/api/materials/search?keyword=steel&minPrice=200&maxPrice=800 HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

### Search Materials by Name Only
GET http://localhost:8080/api/materials/search?keyword=pipe HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

### Search Materials by Min Price Only
GET http://localhost:8080/api/materials/search?minPrice=150 HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

### Search Materials by Max Price Only
GET http://localhost:8080/api/materials/search?maxPrice=300 HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

### Search All Materials (No Filters)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/materials/search HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

### Search with Pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/api/materials/search?keyword=material&page=0&size=5&sort=jobContent,asc HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

### Test Invalid Parameters
GET http://localhost:8080/api/materials/search?minPrice=500&maxPrice=100 HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

### Test Empty Keyword
GET http://localhost:8080/api/materials/search?keyword= HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

### Test Null Parameters
GET http://localhost:8080/api/materials/search?keyword=null&minPrice=null&maxPrice=null HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json